cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.CR

The paper deals with video streaming over highly variable bandwidth conditions, which involves multimedia (cs.MM) and network (cs.NI) aspects. The paper also proposes an optimization problem and algorithm for rate adaptation, which falls under information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV) categories. Additionally, the paper addresses challenges in handling bandwidth prediction errors and short prediction duration, which relates to cryptography and security (cs.CR) as well.
